metadata.name: Fates Disciple
metadata.description:
We were bound by fate, woven together and drenched in colour.....  Nothing cold stop us!

This is the first piece in my new collection [VISIONS](https://foundation.app/collection/bloomvisions?sortOrder=DEFAULT) wherein i dive deep into the practice of exploring the visionary realms through complex symmetry, vibrant colours and multi faceted illustrations.

A disciple stands with eyes closed and arms wide open, she shows herself openly but keeps her words behind her mask.  She embraces the entities around her as she takes in the ways of the cosmos...

Waters flow, scrolls unfurl, candles burn, roses bloom and stars fall... 
She readies herself for a dance with fate..

Be sure to follow my journey here > [WITHERBLOOMS TWITTER](https://twitter.com/WitherBloomArt)

5580 X 5179 px
40.3 MB 
PNG

Upon request the owner of this NFT will receive a high quality copy of the PNG
